<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en">

{{> components/documentHead documentTitle="Thank You"}}

<body id="app-body" class="is-loading">
    <div class="page-wrapper">

        {{> components/header}}

        <section class="section thank-you">
            <div class="container-1180px ta-center">
                <h2 class="ta-center noselect">Thank You ðŸ’˜</h2>
                <div class="container-600px ta-center noselect">
                    <h3 style="font-weight: 100;">
                        You make the app possible!
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <br />
                <p>
                    Thanks to the donations from these generous people, the Assistant for No Man's Sky app is free
                    for everyone to download and use!! These Donations also helped me get this app onto the App
                    Store. To get this app on to the App Store, I had to first purchase an iOS device (an old iPhone
